This is most accurate player ranking system in New Mexico High School Football and here how it works. The "#" next to the athletes name indicates the players overall ranking in the state of New Mexico. Ex. #1 Landry Jones, #2 James Hall, #3 Nathan Enriquez #4 Matthew Sandoval. Rankings! Towards the end of the season, the NMPreps Staff will cut the list down to 8 and then down to a final 4. Throughout the season, we will look back on each week and see how each player has performed. If the player had a monster week, the player will move up on the Mr. Football ladder. If the player gets hurt or has a bad week stat wise (off the field issues count as well) the player will drop a few spots
